  <brief_title>Fermented Milk Drink on Human Intestinal Microflora</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effects of a Fermented Milk Drink Containing Lactobacillus Casei Strain Shirota on the Human Intestinal Microflora</official_title>
  <sponsors>
